[Xie Biyou, Shadow Sect]

00:20:24.590 --> 00:20:25.860
Xie Biyou.

00:20:26.500 --> 00:20:27.240
[Mu Fusheng, Shadow Sect]

00:20:27.240 --> 00:20:28.330
Mu Fusheng.

00:20:29.270 --> 00:20:30.460
[Su Ziyan, Shadow Sect]
Su Ziyan.

